'''[[organic]] [[compound]]'''
#{{chemistry}} any compound containing [[carbon]] [[atom]]s [[covalently]] [[bound]] to other atoms
===Usage notes===
*By convention they do not include the [[carbide]]s, [[carbonate]]s, [[carbon monoxide]] and [[carbon dioxide]]; [[carbon disulphide]] is debatable
===Antonyms===
*[[inorganic compound]]
